  {
   "question": "What are the highest-consensus Restoration Druid items in Phase 4?",
   "answer": "Botanist's Gloves of Growth (70%), Thunderheart Helmet (67%), Thunderheart Tunic (65%). When an item sits above ~70% among top parsers, treat it as the priority drop to chase."
